subject='Welcome to Regeneration Room'
message="Thank you for taking the first step towards a rejuvenated and revitalized you! We're thrilled to confirm your pre-registration for the upcoming Regeneration Room event. Exciting things are right around the corner, and we can't wait to embark on this transformative journey with you.\n\nWhat's Next:\nStay Tuned: Keep an eye on your inbox for exclusive updates, behind-the-scenes insights, and sneak peeks leading up to our opening day.\nSpread the Excitement: Share the news with friends and family who might be interested in joining this rejuvenating experience. After all, transformation is more meaningful when shared!\nPrepare for Wellness: As we approach the event date, we'll be providing tips and suggestions to help you make the most of your Regeneration Room experience.\n\nShould you have any questions or if there's anything specific you're eager to learn about the event, feel free to reach out to us at info@regenerationroom.ca.\n\nGet ready for an unforgettable journey towards a renewed sense of well-being! We're honored to have you as part of the Regeneration Room community."